00:19.083 --> 00:21.542
which mansion will it be,
Gracie or the Governor's?

00:21.542 --> 00:23.291
Head of Crim.
Man, plum purchase.

00:23.291 --> 00:26.500
Freaking launch pad
of the private sector.

00:26.500 --> 00:28.166
I mean, you land it,
you're minted.

00:28.166 --> 00:29.208
