00:31.792 --> 00:33.667
Oh, what the fuck.

00:33.667 --> 00:34.917
Hang for a minute, Bryan.

00:34.917 --> 00:37.125
Listen to what
Bobby has to say.

00:37.125 --> 00:40.291
Come work for Bach's firm,
on my account.

00:40.291 --> 00:43.125
