to grapple with

00:59.667 --> 01:01.959
why you feel happiness
for you can only exist

01:01.959 --> 01:06.000
in the company of hairless
21-year-old girls, come see me.

01:06.000 --> 01:07.834
We can fix that quick.

01:09.208 --> 01:09.875
