the meeting.

01:09.875 --> 01:11.375
Anything for Bruno.

01:11.375 --> 01:14.708
Sandicot's downtown
is ripe for redevelopment.

01:14.708 --> 01:16.750
The whole county's
on the edge of default.

01:16.750 --> 01:17.542
