not at first.

03:43.375 --> 03:45.333
It's some kind of
Albany machine shit.

03:45.333 --> 03:47.750
The kind that's been
going on for 100 years

03:47.750 --> 03:49.208
that we got caught in.

03:49.208 --> 03:51.959
You're getting fottuto  for
something someone's cousin did

03:51.959 --> 03:54.625
to someone else's boss in
a distant part of the state.

03:54.625 --> 03:56.083
