influential young journalist.

04:43.708 --> 04:45.542
Mike, my son Kevin.

04:45.542 --> 04:46.708
Nice to meet you, sir.

04:46.708 --> 04:47.834
Helluva handshake, Kevin.

04:47.834 --> 04:49.375
He's a good kid.

04:49.375 --> 04:51.834
Okay, uh, go out.

04:52.792 --> 04:54.500
Skinny post.

04:54.500 --> 04:56.750
Omaha, Omaha. Hut.

04:57.708 --> 04:59.625
