08:28.667 --> 08:29.792
yes, complete transparency,
but otherwise,

08:29.792 --> 08:32.875
you don't have to share
anything, so you know, go.

08:32.875 --> 08:35.208
Do whatever the fuck you want,
and so will I.

08:35.208 --> 08:37.375
Oh, there it goes.
There it goes.

08:37.375 --> 08:41.792
Your justification...

08:41.792 --> 08:45.125
slid in there so maybe
