it's your only option.

10:26.208 --> 10:26.959
Austerity.

10:26.959 --> 10:29.834
Okay.
Step it out for everyone.

10:31.125 --> 10:34.708
Well, the note exchange requires
that the town pay you first,

10:34.708 --> 10:37.083
