So he was conned
right along with me.

15:19.959 --> 15:22.500
The Gaming Facility
Location Board

15:22.500 --> 15:25.291
reassigned the license
to Kingsford at the last minute.

15:25.291 --> 15:26.583
I confirmed that.

15:26.583 --> 15:29.291
A guy named Joe Scolari
made the call to switch.

15:29.291 --> 15:30.583
No one motivated him?

15:30.583 --> 15:32.375
It's hard to pinpoint
where the idea

15:32.375 --> 15:33.208
to change
even originated,

15:33.208 --> 15:35.792
or who he's trying
to keep happy.

15:35.792 --> 15:36.917
But I do know that
these things don't move

15:36.917 --> 15:38.750
unless somebody orders
it to happen.

15:38.750 --> 15:41.166
Okay.
Stay on it.

15:41.166 --> 15:43.083
I'm gonna get with Scolari,
see if I can get a read on him.

15:50.667 --> 15:53.583
Thank you for agreeing
to meet, Senator Scolari.

15:53.583 --> 15:55.834
Oh, call me Joe.

15:55.834 --> 15:58.792
What brings you up
the Thruway?

15:58.792 --> 16:00.542
You looking for approval
for another,

16:00.542 --> 16:03.208
uh, outdoor shower at your place
in the Hamptons?

16:04.458 --> 16:07.250
Well, if you've gone to so
much trouble to research me,

16:07.250 --> 16:08.417
you must know why.

16:08.417 --> 16:10.500
I'm here as an investor
in New York State

16:10.500 --> 16:12.625
meeting with one its finest
representatives.

16:12.625 --> 16:14.500
Of course.

16:14.500 --> 16:17.875
I know about the note
exchange on Sandicot.

16:17.875 --> 16:20.166
